==English==

===Verb===
'''to [[take]] it [[easy]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[relax]] or [[rest]].
#:''I'm going to stay home Saturday and '''take it easy'''.''

===Expression===
#An [[informal]] [[greeting]] for [[part]]ing or [[closing]].
#:''I'm going home now.  '''Take it easy'''.''

